An Ogudu Magistratesâ€™ Court yesterday remanded 21-year-old Samson Obinna, who allegedly used a toy gun to rob a man of a N40,000 cell phone. Obinna pleaded guilty. Prosecuting Inspector Lucky Ihiehie said the defendant robbed Jude Nworie on the road. According to Ihiehie, Obinna committed the offence on June 6 at 6.30p.m at Mile 12 in Ketu, Lagos State. Magistrate Ejiro Kubeinje adjourned till August 29 for sentencing.